Fix #23: avoid conversions for wall clock

commit.message: mirage-clock-freestanding conflicts with old mirage-solo5 and mirage-xen

Pclock: use caml_get_wall_clock instead of unix_gettime

This avoids conversion between int64, timeval, float, and back to int * int64.
The caml_get_wall_clock is solo5_clock_wall which returns the wall clock time
in nanoseconds since UNIX epoch.
remove travis
